  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    L
    Utility class for logging.
    LengthLimitedVector
    A collection which calls lengthExceeded() when the designated maximum size is reached.
    LRUVector
    Least recently used list of object Each object can be in the Vector a maximum of one time.
    PoolingWeakHashCache
    Objects stored in the WeakRefernce hash table may be garbage collected at any time if the phone needs more memory.
    SortedVector
    A collection which continuously maintains sort order
    SortedVector.Comparator
    A helper class to indicate the sort order for the Vector with the given current data type
    StringUtils
    Utility methods for String operations such as extracting a String from the JAR
    WeakHashCache
    This is a hashtable which acts as a heap memory cache using WeakReference.
